!ZapFonts version 1.03 (04-Nov-00)
==================================

To install, copy !ZapFonts into your boot sequence. For users with a Risc
PC boot structure, it should go in Boot:Resources; otherwise ensure that
it will be booted when your machine starts up.

It is recommended that only one central copy of !ZapFonts should be
present on the system, in order to avoid confusion.

There are is more information about ZapFonts in !ZapFonts.!Help.

Information relating to programming the ZapRedraw module is present in
!ZapFonts.Docs.Redraw, and other ZapRedraw clients should also be aware
of the issues discussed in !ZapFonts.Docs.Usage.

This file may be discarded.
